<section class="content microcase" aria-label="Mini case study">
  <h2>Case: School Christmas Fair</h2>
  <p class="lead">Ben supported a busy school fair stall and helped it run smoothly during peak times.</p>
  <div class="grid grid--two">
    <div class="card" data-reveal>
      <h3>Challenge</h3>
      <p>Short lunchtime window with high footfall, long queues building, and a need to keep the stall merchandised.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card" data-reveal>
      <h3>Actions</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Kept queue flowing and engaged customers with clear next steps.</li>
        <li>Handled cash accurately and reconciled the float at close.</li>
        <li>Maintained tidy counter and attractive display between rushes.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid--two">
    <div class="stat" data-reveal>
      <div class="num">3 hrs</div>
      <div class="muted">Peak shift covered</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat" data-reveal>
      <div class="num">0</div>
      <div class="muted">Till discrepancies</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

